name: Get Lit
description: It's the holidays! That means parties and family get-togethers (which mean DRINKS) - you'll want something festive to wear, so our Get Lit tee with a 'lit up' martini is perfect! This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in both Unisex and Ladies in Black. See size chart for details.

name: Whiskey Makes Me Frisky
description:
If you have a couple shots of Jack and you’re dancing on the bar, then this tee is definitely your style. Or maybe whiskey just makes you irresistible to the ladies. Either way, if whiskey makes YOU frisky, here’s a tee made just for you.

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Charcoal, and Ladies in Coral. See size chart for details.

name: Peace Love Happy Hour
description:
Ahhh, Happy Hour. No matter what kind of day you’ve had, happy hour is the time to relax and hang out with friends while sipping on the adult beverage of your choice. We look forward to it all day and sometimes start happy hour just a little early! Peace, Love, Happy Hour – it’s all we need.

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Storm Grey, and Ladies in White and Frost Pink. See size chart for details.

name: Girls Want Rum
description:
Arrghh, ya scurvy hags! We gals generally don’t like being called hags, but pirates always have RUM! We girly’d up our skull and crossbones with a cute bow and pink eyepatch for all the ladies who love rum. And what’s not to love?!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in both Unisex and Ladies in Black. See size chart for details.

name: Beer Chick
description:
If you search out those places with 100+ beers available on tap, you are most definitely a beer chick. Extra points if you’re a home brewer, too! Or maybe Bud Light is more your speed. Whatever kind of beer you drink, express your love of all things lager (and pilsner and ale and stout and… well, fill in your favorite) and proudly wear the Beer Chick tee!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Cobblestone, and Ladies in White. See size chart for details.

name: Senorita Margarita
description:
Some call it vacation deficit disorder, some say they’re suffering from ‘beachlessness.’ Whatever you call it, here’s the cure: tequila, triple sec, fresh lime juice, lots of ice - and a plane ticket to Mexico? Wherever you are, wear this tee to the first bar you see and you’re good to go!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in White and Ladies in Yellow Haze. See size chart for details.

name: Fill to Line - Margarita
description:
If you’re having one of those “Know When to Give Up and Have a Margarita” days, this is the tee for you. Once you get ‘filled up’ to the line, life will have improved immensely. Plus you’ll be so popular – everyone will ask you where you got this tee!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex and Ladies in Key Lime. See size chart for details.

name: Drink All Day
description:
What a philosophy – or for us, a way of life! Weekends, vacation days, and tailgates mean some bloody marys or screwdrivers will definitely be consumed in the morning hours. And we’re OK with that! If that’s your kind of day, this is your tee.

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Lake, and Ladies in Charcoal. See size chart for details.

name: Get Drunk
description:
Long day at the office? Bad break-up? Yeah, we've all been there. And sometimes having one (or two!) too many is just the thing to get us back in the right frame of mind. Really, sometimes it's OK to say "Maybe We Should Just Get Drunk."

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex and Ladies in White. See size chart for details.

name: Fill to Line - Beer
description:
Who can ever have only one beer? Hanging out with friends at the bar, backyard, boat, or wherever, those cold beers just slide on down. And when you wear your ‘Fill to this line with beer’ tee, the bartender will know to keep ‘em coming!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Gold. See size chart for details.

name: Gin is my Tonic
description:
It’s one of the classiest cocktails – the gin and tonic. That distinct juniper flavor of gin, mellowed by the slight fizz of tonic, a big squeeze of lime delivering that shot of citrus – it’ll cure what ails you. Gin really IS your tonic!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex Key Lime, and Ladies in White. See size chart for details.

name: Also Available in Sober
description:
Some days just get away from you, right? If you’ve slipped just past sober, this tee is for you. We’ll know that sober IS an option for you… just not today! And that the good times will continue. Drink up!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex and Ladies in Charcoal and White. See size chart for details.

name: Breakfast Lunch Dinner
description:
Some days just work out perfectly. A spicy Bloody Mary with breakfast, a dry martini with lunch, a big glass of wine with dinner – yep, that’s a great day. Show off your perfect day in this Breakfast, Lunch, Dinner tee! 

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Ash, and Ladies in Heather Grey. See size chart for details.

name: 30 or 40 Beers
description:
There aren’t many of us that can make it to that 30th beer. OK, we would admit defeat much sooner! But it made us laugh, so we made it into a tee that any beer drinker will love.  

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in both Unisex and Ladies in White or Black. See size chart for details.

name: Vodka is my Tonic
description:
There’s just something about a sunny afternoon and a vodka tonic. With a good squeeze of lime, it’s the ultimate summer refreshment. Or fall refreshment. Winter refreshment? No matter, this tee lets the world know that your tonic is vodka!

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Key Lime, and Ladies in White. See size chart for details.

name: Time Flies Having Rum
description:
Time sure flies when we’re having rum – we’ve lost whole days drinking Anejo on the rocks with a squeeze of lime. Pirates seem to have the same problem, so throw on this tee and be proud of the time you waste drinking rum! 

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in both Unisex and Ladies in Black. See size chart for details.

name: Must Have Rum Punch
description:
Rum punch - the essential island cocktail AND the perfect morning beverage. The problem is we don’t stop drinking them at noon! And we’ll bet you don’t either. This ‘must have’ tee is your ticket to the islands – or to your beach chair at the lake, your seat in the pontoon, your chaise by the pool, your chair at the tailgate … 

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in both Unisex and Ladies in White. See size chart for details.

name: Bike + Beer
description:
After a few miles on the bicycle, doesn’t a beer taste awesome? Hit the trails wearing this tee and everyone will know that you’ve earned that beer. And try to pick a route that has a few ‘destinations,’ if you know what I mean. Like 7 – 8 miles apart?

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in Cobblestone, and Ladies in Heather Grey. See size chart for details.

name: Good to be Tipsy - Cocktail
description:
Feeling a little tipsy? That’s good! Whether your glass of tipsy is filled with beer, wine, or a cocktail, we’ve got you covered. Maybe you need one of each of these tees! Sometimes it’s hard to pick your poison, but it’s easy to just get tipsy. 

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Cocktail available in Unisex in White, and Ladies in Charcoal. See size chart for details.

name: Rum Bum
description:
Do you hide your 7 year Flora de Cana in the back of the liquor cabinet when your rum & coke friends come over? We do too – we’re rum bums! Celebrate all things rum with this fun tee. And tuck one in your suitcase on your next vacation – it just saves time when you’re ordering at the bar.

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Available in Unisex in White and Caribbean Blue, and Ladies in White and Coral. See size chart for details.

name: Good to be Tipsy - Beer
description:
Feeling a little tipsy? That’s good! Whether your glass of tipsy is filled with beer, wine, or a cocktail, we’ve got you covered. Maybe you need one of each of these tees! Sometimes it’s hard to pick your poison, but it’s easy to just get tipsy. 

This shirt is pre-shrunk 5.4 oz. 100% cotton. Beer mug available in Unisex in Lake, and Ladies in Caribbean Blue. See size chart for details.
